## **4.2  Demo Readiness (complete)**

A full rehearsal of the platform against a realistic demo scenario, run end-to-end before any UI polish began. 13 of 14 scripted scenes passed; one was cut with a precisely diagnosed, documented cause rather than papered over.

- **Passed: **core retail (search through refund), personalisation, NDC booking, DCS check-in/boarding, WhatsApp check-in, loyalty earn/redeem, revenue management compute.

- **Cut: **Corporate Travel end-to-end booking — root-caused to a cross-service identity gap between Corporate and Distribution (see ADR-0003, §5 and §6). Not a demo blocker; the fix is scoped as the first task of Workstream 3.

